satlas.basemodel.BaseModel.set_expr¶

BaseModel.set_expr(exprDict)[source]¶

Sets the expression of the selected parameters to the given expressions.

Parameters:exprDict (dictionary) – Dictionary containing the expressions for the parameters with the parameter names as keys.
